Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛  走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之跟我們走就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說要去哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛  走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛  走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長的命令拒絕不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  進去吧  進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有時會發出很可疑的騷動  還會聽到奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感覺到什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…  我也不會感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管夏目你怎麼否認  我始終相信你有種特別的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你並不喜歡  但我覺得那是很了不起的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該更自信一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  說來西村和北本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用去管那些不相信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實像是會有妖怪的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多軌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有意思  我也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  {\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}屜{\r}田同學  我們去對面看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目就去看那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦  行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想跟夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫多軌的小姑娘  還挺機靈的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  我們趕快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地方確實不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼  真的有什麼在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  在對方沒發現我們之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂  你去哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話多軌她們也有危險  我去叫她們回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音  小孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  說不定那不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棺材？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  打開！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裏面？等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就打開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的上勾拳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子怎麼會被關在這裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從氣味來看  似乎不是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在玩捉迷藏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是不小心蓋子掉下來  就出不來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像聽到有聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  沒什麼  你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在這裏  貓咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…興趣真差
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石尾海？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三班那個  就是被怪人追的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還說可能是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是因為父母回家都很晚  他才變得說這種話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被人欺負嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  不知怎麼的他朋友很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BYEBYE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把我關進箱子裏的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說不是我了  我是來給你送東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這傢伙在追著你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看  他還帶著只超醜的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好土！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是豬？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾遠點！豆芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜板！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樸樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人妖！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先逃吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  輕輕鬆鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  海你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉唉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定不會應付小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:43.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（豆芽）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（菜板）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（樸樹）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（人妖）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比跟妖怪對峙受到的傷害還大…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真夠煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好  這個忘記給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  名牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  老師  你幫我帶給那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！居然想用區區200日元就打發我這高貴的妖怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要紙的！紙鈔！給我福澤諭吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（福澤諭吉：萬元鈔）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妖怪追著…那孩子也能看見妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  田沼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見妖怪的孩子…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  也不像被人欺負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了他  那個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是破壞了約定  就吃了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它說的小鬼是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  多軌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裏幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你是第一次見到田沼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是五班的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話等一下再說  趕快離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家裏有書上寫了  說這附近會吸引妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你流血了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候…  是剛才那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血的味道會引來妖怪  快走吧  你也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖輩是陰陽師？所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是很兇暴的妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能對妖怪心軟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它們與人不同  是邪惡的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫海的孩子  真的能看到妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚  不過如果能看到的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想保護他？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到不能坐視不管  就會馬上出手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事  或許是我太傲慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  只覺得是自己在找麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之前  還全都怪在妖怪頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:46.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（你掉的東西）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉…掉的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  會給你的  回去給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又  又是你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪  貓咪～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的興趣真差勁啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟在我後面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是你嗎  不是你在追我  把我關進箱子裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…之前的  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…說你是豆芽  菜板  人妖什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  啊  不…沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見  我道過歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那個追著你的傢伙  告訴警察比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:13:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  跟他們說了也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會沒用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道過歉了  你就別管我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別耍這種無聊的脾氣！等到事情嚴重了就太晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起  我這麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒斷  過幾天就不會痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小孩子弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該如何把我的擔心傳達給他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對妖怪反而交往得更輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想給你添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是剛好看到了  你的手受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想會不會是為了救我  被追著我的傢伙攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次就由我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才跟過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裏人還沒回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一個人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人說要保護我  這還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下  你把我當成什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師是我的保鏢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准忘！也不好笑！真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  小妖怪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追著我來了的話  它的目標就不是海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它盯上海了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  但是它說過要吃掉小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃小孩子的妖怪有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你想太多了  區區小妖怪的戲言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說小妖怪  我剛才還被它弄傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？在我不知道的時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一點小傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子！雖然你被吃掉我就能得到友人帳是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但讓那種小妖怪弄傷我的東西  我心情是很微妙的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常微妙！你懂不懂夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這微妙的心情！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微妙——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那如果海看不到妖怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯上海的不是妖怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰把海關進棺材裏的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真可愛  是在等人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  保護那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以來  我每天放學後都和海一起度過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多軌教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個箱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你不願意就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早些時候  我就覺得被誰盯著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來發現電線桿後面有人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始以為只是變態  就沒太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  這應該在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天  我被那傢伙追趕  跑進了那棟房子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是想躲進那個箱子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果就出不來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子被鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候  我記得沒有鎖…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多軌看不見  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這麼說  夏目也看得見那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多軌  這裏有妖怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶著海往這邊逃  你別追過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…  糟糕  被引過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海  快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.41,0:19:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我放它走的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉的話你會很煩  而且我是個美食家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它的妖氣吸走了不少  應該不會再來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道是這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多軌面無血色地跑來找我  過來一看就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要到什麼時候才會長記性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多軌…是嗎  老師  謝謝你  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別摸鼻子！很癢的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  好厲害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目能馴服妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是馴服  是它救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！海！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多軌！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你們沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多虧了老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了夠了夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海能看見妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼追趕他的是剛才那個妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像還沒結束…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他把海關進棺材裏的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名  名取先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這次特意不想把你捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你自己牽扯過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  把海關進棺材裏的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是關進去  而是封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是不要接近那孩子比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  到底是怎麼回事  名取先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:51.02,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,550)}人與妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海竟然是妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了消滅他才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他幹了什麼！海做了什麼要被人消滅的事嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你也該下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說重要的  到底是人  還是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

